Option 1: VMware Go
===================
VMware Go
A free web-based service that lets users virtualize
their servers with just a few mouse clicks.

VMware Go Pro adds patch management, software license
management, and hardware asset management 
to control assets and secure IT infrastructure.

Launch VMware Go/VMware Go Pro [https://go.vmware.com/]
------------------------------    

This link will take you to the VMware Go web site which
guides users through the installation and configuration
of VMware ESXi.  Please make a note of your license key
as you will be asked for it within 60 days of using
VMware Go.

VMware Go System Requirements
o Windows XP SP3, Windows Vista SP1 or SP2, or Windows 7
o Microsoft Internet Explorer (7.x or 8.x) or Firefox 3.x

