HARDWARE COMPATIBILITY
======================
The latest version of VMware vSphere Hypervisor is based on VMware ESXi 5.0 which is certified 
to run on a broad range of 64-bit hardware.  Check the Hardware Compatibility List to ensure 
that the server model you intend to use is certified to run VMware ESXi 5.0.  For 32-bit 
hardware support, download the previous version of VMware vSphere Hypervisor, which is based 
on VMware ESXi 3.5 and is supported on 32-bit hardware.


